   435	//   node-held box (Solid-async model), so suspense-retry identity is keyed
   436	//   by the NODE, not by which render attempt asked. Interleaved works on one
   437	//   root cannot alias each other's thenables.
   438	// - onRootCommitted(container, batches[], generation) replaces
   439	//   onBatchCommitted(container, token): fanned out per batch id.
