  1355	work" does not hold for it. Both counterexamples are permanent tests: any
  1356	future write-mode-gate optimization must be pre-registered and pass both —
  1357	one asserting the loose default's documented observable behavior, one
  1358	asserting strict-mode parity (17.6).
  1359	
  1360	Either way, the cost story is unchanged: the log entry is cheap (~6 Int32
  1361	stores plus one side-array store), gated at ≤2× a DIRECT write for steady
  1362	logged writes and priced separately for tape-creating writes (18.2).
