    48	## Fresh-checkout recipe
    49	
    50	```sh
    51	git submodule update --init vendor/react   # clones justjake/react @ pinned SHA
    52	cd vendor/react && yarn install --frozen-lockfile && cd ../..
    53	fork/build-react.sh                        # ~13s; build/oss-experimental/{react,react-dom,scheduler}
    54	pnpm install                               # link: overrides resolve to the build
    55	```
    56	
    57	- `fork/build-react.sh` drives `scripts/rollup/build.js` directly
    58	  (`RELEASE_CHANNEL=experimental`, NODE_DEV+NODE_PROD, the 7-entry bundle
    59	  set) and renames `build/node_modules` → `build/oss-experimental`. Node
    60	  version comes from `vendor/react/.nvmrc` via mise when available.
    61	- The workspace consumes the artifacts through `pnpm.overrides` in the root
    62	  `package.json` (`react`/`react-dom`/`scheduler` → `link:vendor/react/
    63	  build/oss-experimental/*`). `link:` means a rebuild is picked up without
    64	  re-running `pnpm install`. No current workspace member depends on react;
    65	  the override binds future `libs/`/`packages/` consumers to the fork.
