    82	
    83	Fetch upstream main in the submodule, branch, `git rebase --onto` the new
    84	base, re-run the fork suite + `fork/build-react.sh`, push, and update the
    85	submodule pin here. The fork suite re-run per rebase is the mitigation the spec mandates
    86	(§4.3); `fork/PLAN.md` §8.5 has the checklist pointer.
